Paper: hep-th/9209104

Date: 1992-09-24

Title: The q-Boson Realizations of the Quantum Group $U_{q}(sl(n+1,C))$

Authors: C. Burdik,L. Cerny and O. Navratil

Comments: 7pp

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A26 (1993) L83-L88

We give explicit expression of recurrency formulae of canonical realizationfor quantum enveloping algebras $U_{q}(sl(n+1,C))$. In these formulas thegenerators of the algebra $U_{q}(sl(n+1,C))$ are expressed by means ofn-canonical q-boson pairs one auxiliary representation of the algebra$U_{q}(gl(n,C))$.